TAG_SPELLS_VERTIGO	TAG_SPELLS		TAG_BARD_2 TAG_BEGUILER_2 TAG_SORCERER_2 TAG_WIZARD_2	Vertigo	~Illusion~[TAG_MAGIC_SCHOOLS_ILLUSION] (Phantasm) [Fear, Mind-Affecting]~Bard~[TAG_BARDS] 2, ~Beguiler~[TAG_BEGUILERS] 2, ~Sorcerer~[TAG_SORCERERS]/~Wizard~[TAG_WIZARDS] 2Components: V, SCasting Time: 1 ~standard action~[TAG_STANDARD_ACTION]Range: Close (25 ft. + 5 ft./2 levels)Target: One creatureDuration: 1 round/levelSaving Throw: ~Will~[TAG_WILLPOWER] disbeliefSpell Resistance: NoThe subject of this spell becomes dizzy, and must make a DC 10 Balance check at the start of each turn or be unable to move. If it fails, it becomes ~unsteady~[TAG_CONDITION_UNSTEADY] and cannot move. If it fails the check by 5 or more, it falls prone. While affected, the subject also takes a -2 penalty to ~attack rolls~[TAG_ATTACK_ROLL] and ~saving throws~[TAG_SAVING_THROW_DESC].
